 results of the CLS model are highly grid-size dependent.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jun 2019 18:09:29 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jun 2020 17:57:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-01"}
