alth care, where strict time constraints place severe\nlimits on measurement strategies. On the conceptual level, our work serves as a\nbridge between wavefront shaping and tunable metasurface design on the physical\nlayer and ML techniques on the processing layer.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 24 Jun 2019 22:12:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-12-09"}
