here it achieves\nstate-of-the-art accuracy with scalability and efficiency. We demonstrate that\nTS-CHIEF can be trained on 130k time series in 2 days, a data quantity that is\nbeyond the reach of any TSC algorithm with comparable accuracy.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jun 2019 05:41:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 14 Feb 2020 04:14:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-02-09"}
