ture network is a weighted ratio of the permeability of the\nfractures and the permeability of the rock matrix, the exact point for the\ncross-over regime is highly dependent on the geometry of the fracture network.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jun 2019 12:19:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-06-26"}
