ed to the\nunique challenges associated with a wide range of applications and data sets,\nproviding a powerful ML-based framework for learning governing models for\nphysical systems from data.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Jun 2019 15:41:15 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 2 Jul 2020 19:24:32 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-06"}
